OL,3,CGuernsey man living in car calls
OL,4,Cisland's homelessness problem 'awful'
OL,6,FA man who lives in his car in Guernsey
OL,7,Fhas called on the island's government
OL,8,Fto do more to support homeless people.
OL,10,FPaul Goddard says he has been sleeping
OL,11,Frough for three years after he lost
OL,12,Fhalf of his property and was refused
OL,13,Fthe financial support he needed.
OL,15,FHe was offered a room to live in and
OL,16,Fraise his children by the government
OL,17,Fbut says the rental cost of the
OL,18,Faccommodation was too high without the
OL,19,Fsupport.
