OL,3,CGuernsey man living in car calls
OL,4,Cisland's homelessness problem 'awful'
OL,6,FPaul told ITV News he was paying
OL,7,Falmost #1,300 per month for the room
OL,8,Fwhile he was only earning #400 per
OL,9,Fweek.
OL,11,FHe says Guernsey's government said
OL,12,Fthis meant he was earning too much to
OL,13,Freceive income support.
