OL,3,CGuernsey man living in car calls
OL,4,Cisland's homelessness problem 'awful'
OL,6,FStates of Guernsey says income support
OL,7,Fis offered to individuals if 'a
OL,8,Fperson's household income is not
OL,9,Fsufficient to meet their needs
OL,10,F(requirement rate) then income support
OL,11,Fwill offer financial assistance to
OL,12,Fbring their household income up to the
OL,13,Frequired level.'
OL,15,FPaul says the cost of the room was too
OL,16,Fhigh for him and the lack of
OL,17,Falternative accommodation on the
OL,18,Fisland left him homeless.
OL,20,FIt was then that he started living in
OL,21,Fhis car.
