OL,3,CGuernsey man living in car calls
OL,4,Cisland's homelessness problem 'awful'
OL,6,FPaul says he knows of other people in
OL,7,FGuernsey living in cars and tents due
OL,8,Fto a lack of affordable social housing
OL,9,Fand financial support.
OL,11,FHe said: "I've seen it quite a few
OL,12,Ftimes. Parked down at Grandes Rocques
OL,13,Fthere was a family living in a car.
OL,15,F"Their baby used to wake up crying
OL,16,Fbetween two and three o'clock every
OL,17,Fnight. There were about two or three
OL,18,Fcars parked down here at one stage."
