OL,3,CGuernsey man living in car calls
OL,4,Cisland's homelessness problem 'awful'
OL,6,FHe added: "I've had a friends living
OL,7,Fin tents. I've had a few friends
OL,8,Fliving in vehicles. It's just awful."
OL,10,FPaul hopes the island's government can
OL,11,Fincrease the amount of support it
OL,12,Fgives to people on low incomes but he
OL,13,Fis not optimistic about the future for
OL,14,Fyoung people living in Guernsey due to
OL,15,Fthe lack of affordable social housing
OL,16,Fand the high cost-of-living.
OL,18,FHe said: "To be honest I feel sorry
OL,19,Ffor the kids growing up over here (in
OL,20,FGuernsey) with the amount and cost of
OL,21,Fproperty and rentals.
