OL,3,CGuernsey man living in car calls
OL,4,Cisland's homelessness problem 'awful'
OL,6,F"Like a child going into a shop or
OL,7,Fsomething like that on a minimum wage,
OL,8,Fthey're going to struggle before they
OL,9,Feven become an adult."
OL,11,FJim Roberts, the Director of
OL,12,FGuernsey's first dedicated
OL,13,Fhomelessness charity for adults, At
OL,14,FHome in Guernsey, also says the
OL,15,Fgovernment needs to do more to prevent
OL,16,Fmore homelessness.
OL,18,FMr Roberts told ITV News: "It
OL,19,Fcontinues to be awful and it looks
OL,20,Flike it might get worse.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G6/12
