OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax     F383A1725303122
OL,3,CGuernsey man living in car calls
OL,4,Cisland's homelessness problem 'awful'
OL,6,F"It's a problem that is largely
OL,7,Finvisible but that can make it more
OL,8,Fdifficult to tackle. That can make it
OL,9,Fmore difficult for politicians to take
OL,10,Fit seriously."
OL,12,FHe added: "The situation is pretty
OL,13,Fstark.
OL,15,F"The fact is, there isn't enough
OL,16,Fsocial housing. There isn't enough
OL,17,Faffordable housing for people to move
OL,18,Finto. The waiting list is very long.
OL,19,FYou can be waiting for years before
OL,20,Fyou're offered social housing so that
OL,21,Fneeds to change.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G7/12
