OL,3,CGuernsey man living in car calls
OL,4,Cisland's homelessness problem 'awful'
OL,6,FHowever, Mr Roberts says that long
OL,7,Fterm solutions to the problem will
OL,8,Fhave to come from "political will".
OL,10,FMr Roberts believes the Committee for
OL,11,FEnvironment and Infrastructure's
OL,12,Frecent Housing Plan update fails to
OL,13,Faddress homelessness urgently enough
OL,14,Fwith work to reduce it only due to
OL,15,Fbegin in 2025.
