OL,3,CGuernsey man living in car calls
OL,4,Cisland's homelessness problem 'awful'
OL,6,FHe wants to see immediate action to
OL,7,Fagree on a statutory definition of
OL,8,Fhomelessness, to understand the exact
OL,9,Fscale of it in Guernsey and to
OL,10,Faccelerate the island's affordable
OL,11,Fhousing programme.
OL,13,FGuernsey's President of Environment
OL,14,Fand Infrastructure, Lindsay de
OL,15,FSausmarez said: "If you look at the
OL,16,Ffactor underpinning homelessness, we
OL,17,Fknow there are lots of different
OL,18,Ffactors feeding into it - it is about
OL,19,Favailability of homes, which is
OL,20,Fsomething we are doing an awful lot on
OL,21,Fin the Guernsey Housing Plan.
