OL,6,F"It is also about affordability and I
OL,7,Fam pleased to say affordability is
OL,8,Fmoving int he right direction
OL,9,Fincluding for people in the private
OL,10,Frental sector who are particularly
OL,11,Fvulnerable to homelessness.
OL,13,F"It is also about security of tenure,
OL,14,Fit is one of the reasons people will
OL,15,Ffind themselves homesless and we are
OL,16,Fdoing a really big bit of work at the
OL,17,Fmoment on security of tenure on the
OL,18,Frights and responsibilities o0f
OL,19,Flandlords and tenants".
